description:
Does God care how I behave? It isn’t by our will or power that we can live Christ-like lives but by the indwelling of the Holy Spirit within us. 

Find the full video about the 22nd Fundamental Belief, “Christian Behavior,” here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cfhk8pyzk6g.
